==English==
===Pronunciation===
*yâ(r)n, /jɑː(r)n/, /<tt>jA:(r)n</tt>/

===Noun===
'''yarn''' (uncountable and countable; plural: [[yarns]])

# a twisted strand of fiber used for knitting
# {{nautical}} Bundles of fibers twisted together, and which in turn are twisted in bundles to form [[strand]]s, which in their turn are twisted or [[plait]]ed to form [[rope]].
# a story, a tale

